        <item>
        <title>彻底解决三星gpsd和lli_pm_wlock耗电问题</title>
        <link>https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 22 Mar 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458647373385.png" alt="Featured image of post 彻底解决三星gpsd和lli_pm_wlock耗电问题" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;三星的安卓手机经常会有莫名耗电快的情况，经过使用better battery stats查看，罪魁祸首就是gpsd与lli_pm_wlock，这两个进程加起来待机一个小时就得耗电10%以上，经过多番查找终于找到解决办法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;gpsd&#34;&gt;gpsd
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;这个原因就是很多app会自动激发定位功能，即使在关闭定位、禁用app调用定位权限掉也没用，app自然会在后台激活gpsd不断尝试定位。解决办法是将gpsd文件设置权限，按照链接中做法，使用gscript控制gpsd开关。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644099541.png&#34;
	width=&#34;800&#34;
	height=&#34;1422&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644099541_hubae408dd63cef9dd4d3404f2c705a2a9_158975_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644099541_hubae408dd63cef9dd4d3404f2c705a2a9_158975_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;image&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;135px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://download.csdn.net/detail/o8xv0123/6881219?web=web&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;http://download.csdn.net/detail/o8xv0123/6881219?web=web&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;lli_pm_wlock&#34;&gt;lli_pm_wlock
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;这是个待机进程，本意是节电的，但是在某种特殊情况下，比如当设置手机信号为仅限4G或者3G，它会不断搜索信号，造成耗电量飙升，解决办法是将手机信号设置为和当地实际情况相符，4G的一定要设置4g/3g/2g自动选择。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644118713.png&#34;
	width=&#34;800&#34;
	height=&#34;1422&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644118713_hu32278cc5a86639ff8c0c55152d803c15_94021_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2016-03-22-samsung/images/wp-1458644118713_hu32278cc5a86639ff8c0c55152d803c15_94021_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;image&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;56&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;135px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://forum.xda-developers.com/showpost.php?p=62519112&amp;amp;postcount=1254&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;http://forum.xda-developers.com/showpost.php?p=62519112&amp;postcount=1254&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
